The construction works of Loft Residences at the Two Rivers Development in Kenya have started following a groundbreaking ceremony by the project’s developer, Centum Real Estate Limited. The project will be carried out by Seyani Brothers & Co., a leading general building construction company in the East African country. Speaking during the groundbreaking ceremony, Samuel Kariuki, the Managing Director of Centum Real Estate affirmed that “Seyani Brothers are a Tier-1 contractor that will ensure that the product is finished to the highest standards & quality and within the stipulated time frame, a promise that Centum Real Estate gives to all its customers.” The construction works are set to be completed by the tenth month of 2022. eval(ez_write_tag([[250,250],'constructionreviewonline_com-medrectangle-4','ezslot_5',115,'0','0']));Loft residences which are designed for the high-end segment of the property market, features 4-bedroom+DSQ duplexes, with each sitting on two levels. Also Read: Construction of “The Alma” in Ruaka, Kenya, resumes eval(ez_write_tag([[250,250],'constructionreviewonline_com-box-4','ezslot_3',117,'0','0']));eval(ez_write_tag([[250,250],'constructionreviewonline_com-box-4','ezslot_4',117,'0','1']));The Centum Real Estate MD said that “this is a high-end product with each unit offering 3,014 square feet of urban elegance. At the heart of the architectural design is a large terrace that opens up to large and expansive private gardens – a first in Kenya for condominium styled living.” The development also features a multifunctional clubhouse, a heated infinity pool, and several jogging tracks within the Two Rivers development. As of October this year, almost half of the units at the Loft Residences had been sold off-plan, a strong indication of the demand for this unique product. The Two Rivers Residential District sits on a 30 acres piece of land within the larger Two Rivers Development. It will comprise 9 unique residential courts three of which are currently under construction. This includes the aforementioned Loft Residences and the Riverbank Apartments and Cascadia Apartments.